Deprecated Interfaces
com.orchestranetworks.schema.ConstraintNomenclature
          since enumeration constraint is more appropriate than this interface when there are many values in the enumeration or when display must be localized. 
 

Deprecated Classes
com.orchestranetworks.d3.D3Engine
          Since 5.4.2, this method has been replaced by D3NodeAsMaster. 
com.orchestranetworks.ui.UIBeanEditorV4
          To use only for backward compatibility of UIBeanEditor implementations written in versions 4.x. One must consider to migrate these implementations as soon as possible.

Deprecated Methods
com.orchestranetworks.ui.UIResponseContext.addComboBox(UIComboBox)
          use UIResponseContext.addWidget(UIWidget) instead. 
com.orchestranetworks.ui.UIBeanEditor.addForPrint(UIResponseContext)
          This method is no more invoked. 
com.orchestranetworks.ui.UITableFilter.addForPrint(UITableFilterResponseContext)
          Use UITableFilter.addForEdit(UITableFilterResponseContext) instead. 
com.orchestranetworks.ui.UIResponseContext.addUIBestMatchingDisplay(Path, UIRenderingMode, String)
          The parameter was used to distinguish the modes 'Display' and 'Print'. Since 'Print' mode is no longer used, it is recommended to use UIResponseContext.addUIBestMatchingDisplay(Path, String) instead. 
com.orchestranetworks.ui.UIResponseContext.addUIListSearch(Path, String)
          Since version 5.3.0, a new combo box is available and is used by default in automatically generated forms. 
com.orchestranetworks.ui.UIResponseContext.addUIListSearch(Path, String, Nomenclature)
            
com.orchestranetworks.ui.UIResponseContext.addUIOccurrenceEditor(Path, String)
          The default occurrence editor can only work with the default multi-occurrence editor. In the UIBeanEditor.addList(UIResponseContext) method, each occurrence can be added with the best matching display/editor with the indexed path obtained with UIContext.getPathForListOccurrence(int). 
com.orchestranetworks.d3.D3Engine.broadcast(VersionKey)
          Since 5.2.7. Replaced by D3Broadcast.broadcast(). 
com.orchestranetworks.interactions.InteractionHelper.complete(InteractionHelper.ParametersMap, Session)

          This method has been replaced by UIResourceLocator.createWebComponentForSubSession().

com.onwbp.adaptation.AdaptationHome.findParent(Adaptation)
          Replaced by Adaptation.getParent(). 
com.onwbp.adaptation.RequestResult.getAdaptation(int)
          It is strongly recommended to use RequestResult.nextAdaptation() instead, as it is safer than this method in the case of concurrent deletion. Moreover, it does not call RequestResult.getSize(), and thus can be less expensive when the iteration is not performed on all records.
